title: UFO Moviez rallies after arm enters cinema tech tie-up
description: UFO Moviez India rose 2.41% after its subsidiary Scrabble Entertainment DMCC entered a strategic tie-up with Shenzhen Timewaying to enhance cinema experiences across the Middle East, India, and SAARC markets.

title: ‘UFO’ spotted over Britain was actually a Chinese space rocket, claim experts
description: A STREAK of blazing light spotted over Britain was a Chinese space rocket and not a UFO, say experts. Witnesses reported seeing the bright pillar at around dawn last Wednesday. Ellie Jarvis, 45, from Clovelly, Devon, was up unusually early when she captured the sight. She said: “I couldn’t believe it. "We’ve seen auroras before,...

title: UFO whistleblower claims Trump was 'fully briefed' on evidence of non-human intelligence
description: A former Air Force major turned whistleblower has claimed President Trump now has the information to change the entire world if he chooses to disclose what the US knows about alien life.

title: Joe Rogan Warns UFO Whistleblowers Need Amnesty Or Truth Will Stay Buried Forever
description: Joe Rogan warns UFO whistleblowers need amnesty to prevent secrets from remaining buried, revealing claims of underwater craft, back engineering, and government cover-ups.
